user: Can I know where I can collect my tickets?
system: You can collect your tickets at the concourse of the train station.
user: What time would the concourse be open?
system: The concourse will be open from 7am to 10pm daily.
user: How far is the train station from the restaurant?
system: It will take approximately 20 minutes by walk and 10 minutes by car.
user: Would I be able to bring pets into the train?
system: No pets are allowed on board the trains.